articles.title: The colloidal stability of albumin-based drug delivery systems has a profound effect on tumoricidal activity.
articles.summary: HSA-PLA nanoparticles improved paclitaxel delivery by enhancing colloidal stability, leading to better tumor exposure and antitumor efficacy compared to Abraxane.
